<subSubSection lastPageId="5" pageId="2" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,151,248]" pageId="2">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,321,151,176]" pageId="2">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
The 
<emphasis box="[385,511,153,176]" italics="true" pageId="2">Notocrypta</emphasis>
species have a very similar phenotype and can be distinguished only by subtle external characters; among them are especially relevant the shape of the forewing white median band and the presence or absence of white subapical small spots on the forewing.
</paragraph>
<caption box="[151,904,1091,1113]" pageId="2">
