<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,1810,1870]" pageId="2">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gallo &amp; Bozano" authorityYear="2017" box="[199,433,1811,1834]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Notocrypta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ariannae">
<emphasis box="[199,433,1811,1834]" italics="true" pageId="2">Notocrypta ariannae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is easily recognizable by two features not found in any of the congeneric species known so far from 
<collectingCountry box="[282,353,1845,1870]" name="China" pageId="2">China</collectingCountry>
:
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1118,1917,1979]" pageId="2">
- the forewing white thin spot projecting distally from the white band (
<figureCitation box="[973,1040,1917,1942]" captionStart="FIGURE 5" captionStartId="3.[151,250,1983,2005]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,232,1937]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[151,1436,193,1962]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURE 5. N. ariannae n. sp. male Paratype, upperside. Scale 2: 1" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1040652/files/figure.png" pageId="2">Fig. 5</figureCitation>
and 
<figureCitation box="[1094,1109,1917,1942]" captionStart="FIGURE 6" captionStartId="4.[151,250,1997,2019]" captionTargetBox="[208,1386,193,1942]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[208,1386,193,1978]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 6. N. ariannae n. sp. male Paratype, underside. Scale 2: 1" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1040654/files/figure.png" pageId="2">6</figureCitation>
) - three minute light spots on hindwing underside discal area (
<figureCitation box="[867,935,1954,1979]" captionStart="FIGURE 6" captionStartId="4.[151,250,1997,2019]" captionTargetBox="[208,1386,193,1942]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[208,1386,193,1978]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 6. N. ariannae n. sp. male Paratype, underside. Scale 2: 1" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1040654/files/figure.png" pageId="2">Fig. 6</figureCitation>
)
</paragraph>
<caption box="[151,833,1983,2006]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1040652/files/figure.png" pageId="3" targetBox="[151,1436,232,1937]" targetPageId="3">
